  "text": "Traced the complete type family for FxVanillaOption across OpenGamma Strata's multi-module Maven project.\n\n## Core Domain Classes (modules/product/)\n\nFound 4 core Joda-Beans domain classes under modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/:\n1. **FxVanillaOption.java** - Base product class annotated with @BeanDefinition, implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxVanillaOption>\n2. **FxVanillaOptionTrade.java** - Trade wrapper for FxVanillaOption, annotated with @BeanDefinition, implements FxOptionTrade and ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade>\n3. **ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java** - Resolved (pricing-ready) form of FxVanillaOption, annotated with @BeanDefinition, implements ResolvedProduct\n4. **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java** - Resolved trade form, annotated with @BeanDefinition, implements ResolvedTrade\n\n## Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\n\nFound 4 pricer classes under modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/ supporting 2 pricing methods (Black and Vanna-Volga):\n1. **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java** - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using lognormal (Black) model\n2. **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java** - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Black model (wraps product pricer and payment pricer)\n3. **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java** - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using Vanna-Volga smile-based method\n4. **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java** - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Vanna-Volga method (wraps product pricer and payment pricer)\n\n## Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\n\nFound 3 measure calculation classes under modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/ that wire pricers to the calculation engine:\n1. **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java** - Implements CalculationFunction<FxVanillaOptionTrade>, routes calculations to measures via FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations\n2. **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java** - Internal class containing the core measure calculation logic, uses both BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer\n3. **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java** - Public API for FX vanilla option trade calculations with DEFAULT instances using both Black and Vanna-Volga pricers\n\n## CSV Plugin Loader (modules/loader/)\n\nFound 1 loader plugin under modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/:\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java** - Implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade>, handles CSV format parsing and writing for FX vanilla option trades\n\n## Barrier Option Embedding FxVanillaOption (modules/product/)\n\nFound FxSingleBarrierOption class under modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/:\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption.java** - Barrier option product that embeds FxVanillaOption as a dependency field (@PropertyDefinition field `underlyingOption` of type FxVanillaOption). This class is also annotated with @BeanDefinition and implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxSingleBarrierOption>.\n\nThe FxVanillaOption type family forms the foundation for both direct vanilla option pricing and as a component of barrier option products in Strata's FX options module."
}

